  "slug": "what-do-i-believe-about-rich-women-journal",
  "title": "What Do I Believe About Rich Women?",
  "subtitle": "A journal prompt set for examining the beliefs about wealth and character that set a ceiling",
  "excerpt": "A journal set for the beliefs (often unexamined) about what it means to be a woman with significant money. Five prompts moving from the gut-level belief to the version of wealth that would feel clean and aligned.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Original journal prompt set written for homemade.education.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal set for the beliefs about wealthy women that run underneath the ceiling. The prompts move from the gut-level belief, through where it came from, to the fear it protects, and toward the version of wealth that would feel clean and aligned.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journal practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What do I actually believe, at gut level, about women who are very wealthy?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write for three minutes without editing. Not what you think you should believe, what you actually believe, including anything uncomfortable.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where did those beliefs come from?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the origin as specifically as you can: a person, a household, a cultural message, something you witnessed. Name the source.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "When you imagine yourself significantly wealthier, what do you notice?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write what arrives, pride, discomfort, fear of visibility, the sense that something would be lost. Name it without judging it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What is the ceiling protecting?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write what you believe would happen if you had significantly more than you do. What is the fear underneath the limit?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the version of wealth that would feel clean and aligned for you.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Not a fantasy, a real picture. What would you do with it, how would it sit, who would you still be? Write the version you are actually working toward.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Written for homemade.education.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
